metadata.name: Kirribilli Palms
metadata.description:
Hello Friends! 

This is my first solo Open Edition.

Taken in the height of the 2020 Covid lockdown. Walking to and from work at the time I noticed this scene and was wanting to capture the right moment. Carrying my Hasselblad with me every day until finally it revealed itself to me. 

This will be available to mint From Dec 25th until my birthday Dec. 31 2022.
